snippet.title: Donald Fuck RPG Stream - 1:1
snippet.description:
Donald Fuck RPG is an interesting piece of work. A long, long time ago, it was known among the RPG Maker community as one of the worst games that had ever been made with the engine.

Recently, a copy has been unearthed from an ancient terrorist burial ground, and its contents were streamed for the detriment of humanity.
